    "16540501175e796680": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "1654050117f10d5d66-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Festival season is about to be in full swing and <em>we can’t wait.</em>",
            "highlight_style": "none",
            "enable_highlight_text_color": false,
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "heading_color": ""
          }
        },
        "1654050117f10d5d66-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Sustainability is the epitome of allure in modern fashion. Our workout wear collection embodies this ethos, seamlessly blending eco-consciousness with undeniable sexiness. From sleek designs to flattering cuts, each piece exudes confidence and style while leaving a minimal environmental footprint. l world where human progress is in harmony with the planet's.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
