        },
        "1654050315a020c10e-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Each piece embodies our commitment to environmental responsibility by repurposing materials that would otherwise go to waste. By utilizing reclaimed cotton, we not only reduce our carbon footprint but also contribute to a circular economy, where resources are reused and recycled. With every purchase, you're not just investing in quality activewear; you're making a conscious choice to support a greener, more sustainable future for fashion.</p>"
          }
        }
